originalText.text: Working with Dennis was an absolute pleasure from start to finish! He takes the time to really get a feel for what you're looking for. Come day of the shoot, he'll have you laughing and having a great time. Not to mention the photo's come out looking AMAZING! Selecting the ones I wanted from the session was the hardest part. Dennis is personable, professional and talented. I highly recommend him.

originalText.text:
I had the pleasure to work with Dennis last week.
I'm an actress and he shot my headshots. I have to say Dennis is the best headshot photographer in NYC area. The shoot was great. Fun and energy - and that's what shows in my pictures, which are purely amazing! Dennis is easy to work with, flawless ethic and from the first second you meet him it just feels like you've known him forever.
Also he is very talented. Just has that artistic eye, that all photographers should have.
I will definitely work with him again!

originalText.text: Dennis is wonderful. He is easygoing, professional and a delight to work with. When my agent wanted specific changes for my head shot look, Dennis delivered that same day. He is skilled, a great listener, and as you can see...a great photographer. Highly recommended!

originalText.text: Dennis is the most relaxed photographer I have ever worked with - which is great because getting new headshots done can be completely overwhelming. He made the process fun and as a result, I had several great shots to choose from. He was flexible with my retouching requests, as well. I HIGHLY recommend Dennis!

originalText.text: I am so happy with my head shots! Dennis went beyond what I asked for and captured some amazing shots! He was very easy to work with and very aware of what casting directors are looking for in a actor's head shot. The finished product is outstanding! He will take the time to make you look human and beautiful.
